Download GlassFish: 
https://idroot.us/install-glassfish-ubuntu-18-04-lts/

To install GlassFish you need Java 8:
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/java
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install oracle-java8-installer

To switch between java versions:
update-java-alternatives --list
sudo update-java-alternatives --set /path/to/java/version
(change /path/to/java/version to the java 8 path)

Start glassfish:
sudo ./asadmin start-domain
(asadmin is in /glassfish5/bin)

Website will be on: localhost:8080
Admin page will be on: localhost:4848

To install Intellij IDEA:
sudo apt install snapd
sudo snap install intellij-idea-community --classic
